Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.83,0:00:05.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And then I suddenly saw my past self.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:10.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to save him, but he made himself fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.24,0:00:12.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Has anything like that happened since?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:14.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was just that one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:16.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.85,0:00:22.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, what's going to happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.45,0:00:24.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can say for sure now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.62,0:00:26.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll prescribe you a sedative.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:29.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Take it if you feel unstable again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:38.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My past self returned once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:43.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,While he was here, I was unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.37,0:00:48.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And while I'm conscious, he's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:54.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if I'm fighting with my past self over the person called Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:01:00.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But he chose to disappear into the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.59,0:01:06.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, he won't try to take over my body again...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:11.93,Dialogue4,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(282,295)}Night in Paris
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.10,0:01:10.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Can I believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.10,0:01:21.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, if we could meet in a dream, could I say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.99,0:01:46.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Say, if sadness alone floats down from the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:54.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If that kind of voice pains you even now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.64,0:01:58.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Even if, off to the side, our hands are placed on each other's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.21,0:02:02.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This memory wouldn't fade, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:10.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Even if, when our eyes meet, I can't say the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:14.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Your words illuminate the world more than anyone else's
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.83,0:02:18.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Next to me, "Goodbye means I love you," you say
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.73,0:02:20.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be forthright
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.37,0:02:22.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Though I alone sing of loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:24.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't smile
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:26.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"Thank you means I'm in love with you," you say
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.98,0:02:31.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The world's end of love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:46.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In the middle of September, I returned to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:51.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I brought with me a ring my mother gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:52.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:57.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.27,0:02:59.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wore this ring when I was younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:02.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You have a girlfriend in Tokyo, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.68,0:03:03.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:06.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But this looks pretty expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:07.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:12.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the ring will be happier being worn by a young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:21.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:24.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:28.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,BANRI!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:30.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:32.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's been such a long, long, super long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.57,0:03:34.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're looking well!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:36.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,When we heard from you, we decided to come meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.71,0:03:38.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:39.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's been way too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:42.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Things just aren't right without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:49.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you people welcoming him home before me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:50.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Know your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:53.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is the moving reunion of two lovers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:56.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:03:57.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:03:59.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:01.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:04.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That joke totally wasn't necessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:07.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home, Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:11.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, welcome, welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:17.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now, a toast to Tada Banri-kun's return to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:19.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:25.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oka-chan, you cut your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:29.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. This is the first time you've seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:30.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:32.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It looks great on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:35.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But wasn't it kind of a shame to cut it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.30,0:04:40.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... you agree with Yana and 2D-kun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:42.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe cutting it was a mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.71,0:04:45.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's a shame at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:47.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it looks great on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:49.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, shucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:51.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:54.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri and Kouko, I need a huge favor from you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:56.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:59.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I could check out your club?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:02.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make a film about the festival club.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:04.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A film?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.23,0:05:05.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:07.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You know the school festival in November?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:09.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want to produce something to show there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:14.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking of editing you guys dancing into a short film, like a music video.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:16.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.51,0:05:18.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oka-chan, are you helping him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:21.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, I've got other plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:24.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to ask the senior members about letting him film us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:25.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:27.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why the festival club, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:31.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to be honest, there's someone in the festival club I'm interested in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:35.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want to film...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:39.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I want to see Linda-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:44.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping this would give me a chance to get closer to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:49.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We've actually gone out to eat together a few times,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:52.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but it's completely one-sided.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:54.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I panicked and did some weird things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:56.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:58.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:01.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the reason, we'll talk to the senior members about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.56,0:06:04.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You just hang on to your one-sided crush and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:06.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.96,0:06:07.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:10.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.40,0:06:11.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So you knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:13.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:17.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We all saw you with Linda-senpai before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:18.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:23.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't all making fun of my one-sided crush, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:25.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:28.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We thought it'd be better if we didn't interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:31.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But it was wrong of us, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:32.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:37.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't tell you guys about Linda-senpai
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:43.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,because there was something else on my mind that wasn't easy to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:44.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could say...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:48.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I actually felt kind of jealous of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:50.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You were jealous of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:57.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,To me, it looks like you and Linda-senpai aren't just in the same club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:07:00.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like there's something else to your relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:05.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,When you got injured,\NLinda-senpai was really worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:08.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And you're both from Shizuoka, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:13.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Once I started thinking about it, everything started to bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:17.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I even thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:21.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,you might be hiding something important from me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:26.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I started to suspect that you didn't really accept me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:31.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be the only time I ask, so give me a straight answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:35.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri, is there something you're not telling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:39.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't I just tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:41.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I should be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:42.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't hide anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:48.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda and I were classmates in high school, and I was in love with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:53.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But I lost my memories, and didn't recognize her when we met again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:59.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've hurt Kouko before because\NI was confused about my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:02.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But now my mind is clear...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:07.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...Linda and my family respect who I am now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:10.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...so everything is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.75,0:08:12.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:16.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,U-um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:17.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:19.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There must really be something wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:22.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for suspecting you of weird stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:23.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No... you weren't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.97,0:08:24.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:28.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I still want to be your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.37,0:08:30.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,S-sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:36.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:39.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just glad you didn't hurt yourself, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:41.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:43.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you something next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:45.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:47.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My mom's ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:50.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:52.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is that something I should give her so casually?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.79,0:08:58.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't giving her a ring mean... proposing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:09:02.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If Kouko and I got married,\NI'd be ecstatic, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:03.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But if we did,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:08.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,the Kaga family fortune and her ramen-eating dad would come with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:14.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I wouldn't fit in as a member of the Kaga family. I just don't match.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:18.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe proposing to Kouko just because I love her is a bad idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:19.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:22.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:23.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:25.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's my present to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:27.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:35.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:37.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.81,0:09:40.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We were apart for a while, weren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:42.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I missed you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:44.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I thought of you all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:47.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but that made me love you even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:48.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,O-okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:55.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd try to express my love artistically, so I made this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:57.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well? What do you think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:10:01.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um... a club?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:05.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's not? Then, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:08.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Eiffel Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:09.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:10.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.47,0:10:15.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-wh-what I'm saying is... you know...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:22.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I decided that when you came back,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.38,0:10:26.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'd f-finally... make you let me get you to become one with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:27.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:31.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, we'll finally climb the stu-ste-stairs to ada-ado-adulthood!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:33.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:35.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just... understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:37.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Understand what I'm saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.80,0:10:45.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kouko, just... Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:45.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I won't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:54.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you to understand... please...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:10:58.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:00.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:06.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:09.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing. I'm fine. Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:12.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:18.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:20.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I had too much to eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:26.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:26.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I swallowed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:27.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Swallowed what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:30.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine now, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:41.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why did it turn out this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:43.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:46.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's the kind of thing I'd expect from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.13,0:11:48.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is what you expect of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:49.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.34,0:11:52.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want it to be more romantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:56.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But this is how I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:59.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You keep drawing this side of myself out of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:03.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is the one place where I can truly be myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:09.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I belong here more than I belong in my own room at my own house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:11.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.86,0:12:14.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one I want to come home to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:19.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've been searching for this place for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.47,0:12:23.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri, you've finally fallen for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:25.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I have, I definitely have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:30.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take things at our own pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.28,0:12:32.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We have plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:33.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.12,0:12:42.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Our second semester classes started.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:44.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It was autumn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:49.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The festival club had begun practicing for its next festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:52.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yanagisawa Mitsuo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:54.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's apparently Banri and Roboko's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:55.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for having me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:12:57.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Any objections or questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:58.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:13:00.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yanagisawa-kun, do you have a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:02.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,N-no, I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:04.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:06.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We might finally have a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:07.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do? What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:11.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys, I don't have a girlfriend, either. What'll you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:12.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:14.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're not doing anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:17.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, looks like no one's opposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:20.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Try to work with Yanagisawa-kun, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.83,0:13:22.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:25.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot going on this fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:26.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,First, October.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:29.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's another Awa dance festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:31.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,After that is the school festival in November.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:34.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be asking people from other colleges for backup there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:36.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Give it everything you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:36.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:38.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, start warming up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:43.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's great that you got permission, Yana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:45.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.86,0:13:51.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:55.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I made Linda-senpai mad the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:13:58.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:01.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kouko-chan, let's warm up together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:02.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.44,0:14:10.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's all for today's practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:12.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:13.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Good work today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:17.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:20.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get the chance to say a single word to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:22.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:24.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There are almost two months before the school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:32.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've been summoned to a really secret conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:33.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,About Mitsuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:34.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:36.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:39.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Leave Mitsuo to me. I'll stall him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:43.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mitsuo, why don't we get some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:45.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? With you? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:46.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And where are you going, Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:50.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I need to go get something I forgot on campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:52.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'd feel bad making Kouko come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:54.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you hang out with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:56.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let us come, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:58.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We want to know more about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:01.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we want to know every last thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:02.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.93,0:15:06.56,Dialogue3,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(91,317)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Pick up after
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.93,0:15:06.56,Dialogue3,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(90,344)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}your dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:06.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:08.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:10.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:15.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-what, specifically, are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:17.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:19.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't know what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:21.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.95,0:15:23.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be unreasonable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:25.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,When you say that to me with that look on your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:26.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:29.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You kicked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:29.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Yeah, I kicked you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.52,0:15:32.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I really don't know what you meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:35.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so pissed about Yana-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:36.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:38.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:40.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Would you kick my butt on the street if you weren't mad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:43.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,See? Those eyes...! You're mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.14,0:15:46.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:48.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm not mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:49.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:51.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:53.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I s-s-s-s-seriously don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:16:02.85,Dialogue3,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(69,302)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Pick up
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:16:02.85,Dialogue3,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(67,321)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}after your dog
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:16:00.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, you idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:01.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:02.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:06.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe how stupid you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:08.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, it's unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:12.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm thinking from the bottom of my heart that you're a major idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:13.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:16.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:23.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what campus is like after classes are over...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.65,0:16:30.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.19,0:16:33.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:35.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was just really surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:36.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I got flustered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:38.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That Yana-san came?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.03,0:16:40.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.50,0:16:43.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You should have told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:46.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you want to avoid Yana-san so badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:48.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I want to avoid him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:52.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you might have heard from\NYanagisawa Mitsuo, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.34,0:16:57.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He treated me to dinner a few times over summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:59.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:03.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him a few times working at the club,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:07.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,and I thought it'd be fun to spend time with a younger guy now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:11.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But one day, I suddenly wondered, "Why?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:12.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:18.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he seem so happy having dinner with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:25.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm being self-conscious, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.07,0:17:28.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Heck, it doesn't matter what you think of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:34.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like Yanagisawa Mitsuo saw me as something really precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:37.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it was kind of scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.15,0:17:38.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:41.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A big, sweet, pedigreed dog of a guy like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:45.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I couldn't tell what about me he was interested in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:48.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If it was a fantasy, a misunderstanding, or an assumption...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:51.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:54.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he just likes you because you're attractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:56.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.00,0:17:58.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a prettier face than mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:03.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,and I don't think I've shown him enough of my personality for him to fall in love with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:07.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I don't want him to think he knows me after spending so little time with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:12.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So, I thought I'd keep my distance for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:14.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Then, today...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:17.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kouko and I brought him to the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.69,0:18:19.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It really threw me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:22.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:24.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start by killing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:27.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Then... I'll send Kouko after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.70,0:18:29.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I was thinking during practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:32.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I distinctly felt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:34.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm just taking out my anger on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:38.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about kicking you in the butt earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:38.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:41.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm totally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:43.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.32,0:18:47.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I always get so weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.86,0:18:49.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So basically,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:53.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,you're actually kind of interested in Yana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:54.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:18:57.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really pissed at you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:58.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you making that face?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.13,0:19:01.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just because you have a girlfriend, you think you can say whatever you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:04.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! I'm sorry, I'm sorry, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:10.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You and Kouko-chan seem to be getting along as well as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:12.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Was she lonely while you were in Shizuoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:15.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:16.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to talk to you about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:20.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.35,0:19:21.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:25.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My mom gave me her ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:26.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Her ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:29.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She told me to give it to my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.03,0:19:34.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm going to give it to her,\NI thought I'd wait for the right situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:35.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't found the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:39.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the ring you were supposed to give me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:40.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.77,0:19:41.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:42.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:45.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! I'm sorry, I'm sorry, I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.11,0:19:46.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:51.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But your mom must be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:56.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a girlfriend out here, and you're doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:59.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:00.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:02.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:03.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Have some confidence in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:06.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But I haven't been able to tell my friends yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:10.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,About my past... including you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:15.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yanagisawa Mitsuo doesn't know about us either, does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:18.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not trying to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:21.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But you didn't say anything, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:24.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want him to feel weirdly about you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:27.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.05,0:20:27.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:29.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:32.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Everything, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:34.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Guess that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:36.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:38.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.23,0:20:41.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing out so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:43.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Linda-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.94,0:20:46.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Are you Banri's friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.84,0:20:47.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:49.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Oka Chinami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.98,0:20:53.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri, do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:20:54.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:56.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll head back, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:20:58.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oka-chan, I hope we can talk sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.25,0:20:59.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'd love to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.96,0:21:09.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oka-chan, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:12.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was helping some upperclassmen from the film club.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:15.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Banri, what was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:16.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:18.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:21.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so close with Linda-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:22.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.81,0:21:26.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the same club, and we have a lot in common...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:27.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:29.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's the girl Yana-san likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:32.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's not right for you to be so close to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.99,0:21:34.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.22,0:21:36.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think you're acting a little weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.49,0:21:38.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason for you to be so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:39.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're the weird one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.99,0:21:45.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I think Kaga-san would feel bad if she saw you two just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:47.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel bad for Kaga-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:50.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:15.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong, I'm telling you you're wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.40,0:22:18.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you still don't notice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.57,0:22:24.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Though I've wanted to touch that arm for the past two or three hours
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.91,0:22:28.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I do not need forever love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.24,0:22:31.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot believe forever love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.85,0:22:38.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The urge to scream is so great that, look, I can't stand it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.52,0:22:44.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So why, why won't you notice even a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.69,0:22:51.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really, really in love with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.90,0:22:57.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need words of flattery
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.90,0:23:00.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Love me semi-eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.14,0:23:04.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,After 5,000 years or so, I won't be interested
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.21,0:23:07.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not endless
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:11.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I will die someday
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.15,0:23:17.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Being told "I'll love you forever" won't make me happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.56,0:23:21.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,First, think only that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.33,0:23:25.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You'll love me till I die
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.00,0:23:40.98,Dialogue4,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(55,410)}His Chasm
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.07,0:23:28.07,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(233,366)}Kouko, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.07,0:23:31.77,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(56,362)}W-we'll finally climb the ste-sto-stairs to adulthood...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.77,0:23:32.77,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(291,366)}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.77,0:23:33.94,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(244,366)}It's only a little sour.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.94,0:23:36.61,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(167,366)}This is...! The spice...! Of love...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.61,0:23:38.01,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(272,365)}Banri, smooch!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.01,0:23:40.98,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(181,366)}I... I'll have some of that spice!
